snippet.title: Phantasy Star Zero - Eternal Tower (Normal) All 101 Floors
snippet.description:
The complete playthrough of the Eternal Tower quest on Normal difficulty. Edited out trips back to town to restock, and anytime I may have gone AFK. It's a 5+ hour quest, so who can blame me. 

Rendered in Sony Vegas for 12 hours, for a total of 82GB video. Enjoy.
